370
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:55,950
Vieš ktorú, však?

371
00:23:57,330 --> 00:24:01,510
Každý sa bude báť. Vrátime sa?

372
00:24:01,510 --> 00:24:02,900
Áno.

373
00:24:06,970 --> 00:24:09,480
Eun Chae!

374
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,980
Jeong Eun Chae.

375
00:24:11,980 --> 00:24:14,310
Eun Chae!

376
00:24:51,390 --> 00:24:52,880
Už sú tu.

377
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:56,480
Si v poriadku?

378
00:24:57,340 --> 00:24:59,330
Mrzí ma,
